            </div>
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-white/90 to-white/70 p-5 rounded-xl backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/30 hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
              <div class="text-2xl mb-2">⏱️</div>
              <div class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-1">Autonomie</div>
              <div class="text-gray-600 text-sm">72 heures d'utilisation</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-white/90 to-white/70 p-5 rounded-xl backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/30 hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
              <div class="text-2xl mb-2">⚡</div>
              <div class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-1">Temps de charge</div>
              <div class="text-gray-600 text-sm">2 heures (boîtier inclus)</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-white/90 to-white/70 p-5 rounded-xl backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/30 hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
              <div class="text-2xl mb-2">📡</div>
              <div class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-1">Connectivité</div>
              <div class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Bluetooth 5.0</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-white/90 to-white/70 p-5 rounded-xl backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/30 hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
              <div class="text-2xl mb-2">📱</div>
              <div class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-1">Compatibilité</div>
